#. module: cyllo_asset_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_asset_leasing
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_asset_rental
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding:0px;\">\n"
"                <div>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('customer') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    I hope this email finds you well. We are pleased to confirm the leasing arrangement for the\n"
"                    following asset:\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Asset Name:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('asset') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    Lease Start Date:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('start_date') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Lease End Date:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('end_date') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    As per the agreement, please ensure timely payment of the lease fees and adhere to the terms\n"
"                    outlined therein.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Should you have any questions or require further clarification regarding the lease\n"
"                    agreement, feel free to contact us at your convenience.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Best regards,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div style = \"marge: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"<div>\n"
"Beste\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('klant') of niet_available\">, </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ik hoop dat deze e -mail je goed vindt.We zijn verheugd om de leasing -regeling voor de\n"
"volgende activa:\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Activanaam:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('activa') of niet_available\"> </t>\n"
"LEASE START DATUM:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('start_date') of niet_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Lease -einddatum:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('end_date') of Not_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Volgens de overeenkomst zorg je voor tijdige betaling van de leasekosten en houd je aan de voorwaarden\n"
"Daarin geschetst.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Mocht u vragen hebben of verdere opheldering nodig hebben met betrekking tot de huurovereenkomst\n"
"Overeenkomst, neem gerust contact met ons op uw gemak.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Als u vragen heeft of verdere hulp nodig hebt, aarzel dan niet om contact met ons op te nemen.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Hartelijke groeten,\n"
"<br>\n"
"</div>\n"
"</div>"

#. module: cyllo_asset_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_leased_assent_return_reminder
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding:0px;\">\n"
"                <div>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('customer') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    This is a friendly reminder regarding the return of the leased asset,\n"
"                    <b>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"ctx.get('asset') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    </b>\n"
"                    , which is due\n"
"                    for return as per our lease agreement on\n"
"                    <b>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"ctx.get('end_date') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    </b>\n"
"                    .\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Please ensure that the asset is returned on or before the specified return date to avoid any\n"
"                    potential late fees or penalties as outlined in our agreement.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Best regards,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div style = \"marge: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"<div>\n"
"Beste\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('klant') of niet_available\">, </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Dit is een vriendelijke herinnering met betrekking tot de terugkeer van het gehuurde actief,\n"
"<b>\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('activa') of niet_available\">, </t>\n"
"</b>\n"
", dat is verschuldigd\n"
"voor terugkeer volgens onze huurovereenkomst over\n"
"<b>\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('end_date') of Not_available\">, </t>\n"
"</b>\n"
".\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Zorg ervoor dat het actief wordt geretourneerd op of vóór de opgegeven retourdatum om een ​​te voorkomen\n"
"Potentiële late kosten of boetes zoals in onze overeenkomst beschreven.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Als u vragen heeft of verdere hulp nodig hebt, aarzel dan niet om contact met ons op te nemen.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Hartelijke groeten,\n"
"<br>\n"
"</div>\n"
"</div>"

#. module: cyllo_asset_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_assent_rental_invoice_due_reminder
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding:0px;\">\n"
"                <div>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('customer') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    This is a friendly reminder regarding the upcoming payment for the rental asset invoice.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    As per our agreement, the payment for the asset\n"
"                    <b>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"ctx.get('asset') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    </b>is due on\n"
"                    <b><t t-out=\"ctx.get('due_date') or not_available\">,</t></b>\n"
"                    . However, it appears that\n"
"                    the payment has not yet been received.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Please ensure that the payment is made promptly to avoid any late fees or disruptions to your rental\n"
"                    agreement. Your cooperation in this matter is greatly appreciated.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have already made the payment, please disregard this reminder, and kindly inform us of the\n"
"                    transaction details for our records.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Best regards,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div style = \"marge: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"<div>\n"
"Beste\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('klant') of niet_available\">, </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Dit is een vriendelijke herinnering met betrekking tot de komende betaling voor de factuur van de huuractiva.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Volgens onze overeenkomst, de betaling voor het actief\n"
"<b>\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('activa') of niet_available\">, </t>\n"
"</b> is verschuldigd\n"
"<b> <t t-out = \"ctx.get ('due_date') of not_available\">, </t> </b>\n"
".Het lijkt er echter op\n"
"De betaling is nog niet ontvangen.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Zorg ervoor dat de betaling snel wordt gedaan om late kosten of verstoringen van uw huur te voorkomen\n"
"overeenkomst.Uw medewerking in deze kwestie wordt zeer op prijs gesteld.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Als u de betaling al hebt gedaan, negeer dan deze herinnering en informeer ons vriendelijk over de\n"
"Transactiegegevens voor onze gegevens.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Als u vragen heeft of verdere hulp nodig hebt, aarzel dan niet om contact met ons op te nemen.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Hartelijke groeten,\n"
"<br>\n"
"</div>\n"
"</div>"

#. module: cyllo_asset_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_asset_assignment
msgid ""
"<div>\n"
"                <div>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('employee') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    I hope this email finds you well.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    I am pleased to inform you that the following asset have been assigned to you:\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Asset Name:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('asset') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Assign Date:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('assign_date') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Please take good care of the assigned asset and ensure they are used responsibly in accordance\n"
"                    with our organization's policies and guidelines.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Should you encounter any issues or have any\n"
"                    questions regarding the assigned asset, please feel free to reach out to us for assistance.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Best regards,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div>\n"
"<div>\n"
"Beste\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('werknemer') of niet_available\">, </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ik hoop dat deze e -mail je goed vindt.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ik ben blij u te kunnen informeren dat het volgende actief aan u is toegewezen:\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Activanaam:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('activa') of niet_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Datum toewijzen:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('CODUCT_DATE') of Not_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Zorg alsjeblieft goed voor het toegewezen actief en zorg ervoor dat ze op verantwoorde wijze worden gebruikt in overeenstemming\n"
"met het beleid en de richtlijnen van onze organisatie.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Mocht u problemen ondervinden of heeft een\n"
"Vragen over het toegewezen actief, aarzel niet om contact met ons op te nemen voor hulp.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Als u vragen heeft of verdere hulp nodig hebt, aarzel dan niet om contact met ons op te nemen.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Hartelijke groeten,\n"
"<br>\n"
"\n"
"</div>\n"
"</div>"

